This bot automatically posts announcements in Discord when events from the schedule spreadsheet are about to start. To run it, activate the virtual environment with venv\Scripts\activate (Windows) 
or source venv/bin/activate (Mac), then run pip install -r requirements.txt, navigate into the src folder, and run python main.py. 
Make sure your .env file has all the required credentials — ask a teammate for the values. 
To add or edit events just update the Google Sheet directly, the bot checks it every 30 seconds. Press Ctrl+C to stop the bot.
